    "body": "openmpi should depend on the compiler used by the wrappers.  I managed to gc the one built into the wrappers.\r\nI can't immediately see how to get it into the dependencies, but I assume it's simple.\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\nBuild openmpi with a new compiler, uninstall that compiler, and try to run mpicc.\r\n\r\n### Information on your system\r\n\r\nSpack v0.16.0, openmpi commit 77b2e578ec47f7713cae965fede1ab6e60aa69c4\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\n\r\n@hppritcha\r\n",
